Hi All,

I am the OP of this issue, just registered to provide more info;
@kodiakhub Thanks for your help to diagnostic the issue is from this rule, it is actual a danger rule, the content is blocked because someone left a comment with the key word "広告"( and the comment is now gone so cannot reproduce), these word does have many meaning in Japanese not just mean "sponsored", in the original comment the user mean to "spread the topic", also found the keywords in the rule is google translated word not match "sponsored" in my system language.

@Alex-302 Thanks for your help, I have temporary disable this rule to show the content, could this rule make more specific to exclude comment text?

